============================================================

The improvement plan is written to `tools/title-loop/docs/26-e8ee23c/improvement-plan.md`.

**Summary of the 5 targeted fixes for 16 generated-file failures:**

1. **Expand OCR repair dictionary** (+50 common English words like `with`, `dip`, `pie`) — fixes Patterns B (2) and C (3)
2. **Relax section-label merge blocking** for single-word continuations after short ALL_CAPS fragments — fixes Pattern E (1)
3. **Improve spillover handling** in `findBurstEnd` with better post-marker skipping — fixes Pattern A (5)
4. **Strengthen first-after-preamble bonus** from +0.08 to +0.12 when preamble contains section labels — fixes Pattern D (3)
5. **Fix mid-recipe detection**: Unicode fractions in `startsWithNumber` + body-prose detection in `isTitleAbsentPage` — fixes Pattern F (2)

All changes are within existing pipeline stages — no architectural changes. Real file accuracy (100%) should be unaffected.
